---
import Carrusel from '../components/Carrusel.astro';
---
<header class="relative flex flex-col items-center max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto md:flex-row sm:px-6 p-8">
    <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-1/2 md:pb-20 md:pt-10 md:pr-10">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1
                class="animate-fade-down animate-once text-4xl font-extrabold leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl sm:leading-none md:text-6xl">
                Dojo
                <span class="font-bold text-rose-900">Escuela de artes marciales</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl md:max-w-3xl">
                Descubre el equilibrio entre la fuerza y la serenidad, la disciplina y la creatividad. Únete a nosotros en el Dojo y haz del arte marcial no solo una práctica, sino un estilo de vida que transforma y enriquece
            </p>
            <div class="mt-5 sm:flex md:mt-8">
                <div class="rounded-md shadow"><a href=""
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-full px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium leading-6 text-white transition duration-150 ease-in-out bg-rose-900 border border-transparent rounded-md hover:bg-rose-800 focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline-blue md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
                        Contactanos
                        <div class="m-1">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-brand-whatsapp" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M3 21l1.65 -3.8a9 9 0 1 1 3.4 2.9l-5.05 .9" /><path d="M9 10a.5 .5 0 0 0 1 0v-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 -1 0v1a5 5 0 0 0 5 5h1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 -1h-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 1" /></svg>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3 rounded-md shadow sm:mt-0 sm:ml-3">
                    <a href=""
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-full px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium leading-6 text-rose-900 transition duration-150 ease-in-out bg border border-transparent rounded-md hover:text-rose-800 focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline-blue md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10">
                        Llamanos
                        <div class="m-1">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-phone" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M5 4h4l2 5l-2.5 1.5a11 11 0 0 0 5 5l1.5 -2.5l5 2v4a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2a16 16 0 0 1 -15 -15a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2" /></svg>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-1/2 md:pb-20 md:pt-10 md:pl-10">
        <div class="relative w-full p-3 rounded  md:p-8">
            <div class="rounded-lg bg-white text-black w-full">
                <Carrusel/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>